/DEV : 

    LIST DEVICES : ls /dev


/SYS : 

    LIST DETAILS OF DEVICES : ls /sys/Disk/Partition


UDEV : 

    CREATE DEVICE NODE : mknod /dev/Disk_Partition Type Major  Minor


LIST USB DEVICES : lsusb

LIST PCI DEVICES : lspci

LIST SCSI DEVICES : lsscsi


DD : 

    CONVERT AND COPY DATA : dd if=/Input_File/Path of=/Out_File/Path bs=Block_Size_INT count=COUNT_INT

        if = INPUT FILE
        oF = OUTPUT FILE
        bs = WRITE THESE NUMBER OF BYTES AT A TIME
        count = NUMBER OF BLOCKS TO COPY




